data.description: Lovely bedroom community near Diablo Grande freeway entrance, good shopping, restaurants, golf course and many other fine amenities.  This large 3 bed 2 bath home has good flow and charming design lay-out. The Home ownership community covers the common landscaping areas maintenance including watering, playground and personnel at the entry gates for your security and prestige. Make your appointment today, home will not last long!
